<p>
<lb n="1"/>vekutāṉiya varu<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>m taiy mātam <hi rend="grantha">3 §</hi> Āṉaikonti veṅkaṭapatirāyar
<lb n="2"/>ṉāḷil cavāmaṉāṟaṇappa ṉāyakkar Elumaṭṭiyil kuruvāvattākac cālai
<lb n="3"/>Apparukku viṭṭa caṟuvamāṉiyam kūvattil tiṟipuvaṉamātevi viḷākattil
<lb n="4"/>maṇali kiḻakku <num value="16"><g type="numeral">10</g> 6</num> paccilānettam kiḻakku <num value="34">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num> periyanaṅkai taṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kiḻakku <num value="50">5 <g type="numeral">10</g></num> Āka<num value="100"><g type="numeral">100</g></num>
<lb n="5"/>yinta kuḻi ṉūṟum Ūravarukkup puṇṇiyamāka kaṭṭaḷaiyiṭṭom yintapaṭi<hi rend="grantha">kk</hi>u
<lb n="6"/>yinta māṉiyattukku vikātam paṇṇiṉavarkaḷ keṅkaikkaraiyil kārāmpacuvaik ko
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṉṟa to<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ttile poka kaṭavarākavum §
</p>

